des:
Newburgh Envelope is a local, family owned and operated print shop in Newburgh New York. For four generations Newburgh Envelope has been helping entrepreneurs access affordable marketing materials to launch their businesses. Medium to Large companies trust Newburgh Envelope to print and warehouse their most needed items including envelopes, letterhead, folders, business and appointment cards. New products are being added including advertising flags, small signage, banners and table throws. Call Amy, the Paper Princess today.
